        <abstract> 
<p>Although CD’s experiments with pepsin were unsuccessful, he observed that the glands [of <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>] as far as acid is concerned act just as the stomach of a mammal. Further experiments detailed. The secretion must contain something analogous to pepsin. [See <hi rend="doubleUnderline">9062</hi>.]</p> 
        </abstract>
